# FS25 Farm Dashboard mod — repack after Lua changes

The game loads **`FS25_FarmDashboard.zip`** (or an extracted folder) under **`mods/`**. Edits under `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/src/` are **not** picked up until you rebuild the archive (or copy files to the server’s mod tree).

From repo root **`FarmHub`** (parent of `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod` and `tools`):

```powershell
.\tools\Zip-FarmDashboardMod.ps1
```

Output: **`FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard.zip`** with **`modDesc.xml`**, optional **`icon.png`**, and **`src/`** at the **zip root** (no extra wrapper folder). Upload/replace on dedicated host and restart if needed.
